Do you like the life in big city ? I do not like to life in big city. crowded (traffics), noisy but once i  choosed to pursuit higher education. I have to adapt /get used to new environment.  
What do you like about living in the big city ?. It has many public buildings like hospitals, schools, parks, ... I can always find i need. It is convinient. Living in the big city offers high life quality/ living standard. I have an access to better education, job opportunities, salary, healthcare system, ...
Do you think the environment is one of the most serious problem in big city ?
Yes, absolutely. thesedays, living in urbanization era, metropolitians (=big city) are overpopulated. This leads to huge traffics, wastes, ... This contaminates the air, water, ... Pollutiton causes health problems like respiratory, asthma, ... 
-> The environment is polluted badly, especially the air, water, ... this do harm to citizen health. potentially causing respiratory, asthma, ...  
What are the sollutions ?. 
-> government: (the government should impose some regulations, penalty, policies on preserving the environment -> for example, In singapore, the government has warned the citizen not to throw rubishs without permission, if people go againist the rules, they will charged 20 dolas. The government can also invest on sustainable energy, like wind and solar energy,   
-> individual: (individual should adopt green lifesytle. peope should avoid using plastics, recycle and reuse more, ... from my own experiences, ____ 
If my memories serve me right (neu tri nho toi dung).
Do you prefer to live in bigcity or countryside ?
I prefer to live in countryside because it is peaceful. 
I am currently living in big city (li do) -> _Big city has fast-pacing lifestyle. Everyone always pursuit achivement so that why they spent a lot of time on their work. Sometimes they often forget to spent time for themselve and their familiy. Moreover, the traffics are crowded and noisy, especially during peaked/rush hour.
Overal, despite the life in big city is more convinient and fulfilling but i would like to have work-life blance with my family and friends. 















 

