</p><br><p><strong>Q: When do you go to the beach and why?</strong></p><p>Answer: Have you ever traveled to any beaches ?. 
Do you love beach ? -> yes, definitely, it helps me relaxing and disconnect from work and daily routine.
How do you feel about the nature in Da Nang beach city ?.
+) weather. -> The local weather is very nice. It is hot, sunny and windy on summer so it is ideal for swimming, sunbathing. 
+) nature -> Da Nang also has white sand, blue clean water, tall greeny coconut trees, many island far away,  so romantic and stunning.
How do you feel about people in Da Nang ?.
friendly and hospital. they recommned best seller dishes, market,  
What about buildings ?. 
There are many skyscrapers in Da Nang, full of modern buildings. Tourist can access to shopping malls, amusment park, aquarium, restaurant, ... I can always find what i need . It is very conivient when the city have many to offer.
What do you often do when you go to the beach ?.
On the beach, i often sit on the sand, lie on towel, go swimming and sunbathing, watch the wave, take photo with friends. 
Do you prefer to go alone or with friends ?.
I prefer to go with friends because we can explore the retaurant, try on new dishes, sight-seeing many destinations, take a photo, upload on social media to keep the memories last forever. Moreover, if i travel online and meet unwanted situations, i can not seek for any helps, so go with friend will be more safe.












